      • AbstractReaderDto

        public AbstractReaderDto(java.io.BufferedReader reader)
        Create a DTO object reading from a tab-delimited line. The client is responsible for opening and closing the reader. The client should catch the EndOfStream throwable to determine when reading is complete and to then close the reader.
        Parameters:
        reader - the buffered reader set at the current line to read
